{"3166070": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "被動勇者：100天拯救世界！", "steam_appid": 3166070, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/e39f71af00b69421592fb853c41a07be.avif?t=1773240105\" width=617 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被一位自稱掌管生命與豐饒的女神選中，召喚到了異世界！<br>然而，正當你準備大展拳腳時，她卻毫不慌張地丟下一個驚天炸彈：這個世界將在 100 天後被魔王毀滅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更糟糕的是，她的魔力在召喚你時被耗盡，所以：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     1. 她完全不知道魔王是誰、在哪裡、又有多強；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     2. 你只能使用被動技能；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     3. 她經常用「沒魔力了」當藉口偷懶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這場拯救世界的旅途，從一開始就絕望又奇怪——但你並非孤軍奮戰。<br>這位廢柴女神決定陪你一起上路！<br>奇怪的是，她身上偶爾會散發出一種……海鮮的味道？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最後的 100 天裡，探索這個瀕臨毀滅的世界，結識性格各異的夥伴，展開一段無法預測的冒險吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/8e703a1cd09633dd5aa0fcf624d4ae3f.avif?t=1773240105\" width=617 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.poster.avif?t=1773240105\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.webm?t=1773240105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.mp4?t=1773240105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_